features: 【3 Drawer Design】The table top measures 18" L x 14" W, and each drawer measures 14.3" L x 11.2" W x 2.6" H. The tabletop is large enough to hold a photo frame, lamp, or decoration. 3 wide drawers can store a variety of items such as remote controls, manicure kits, shavers, hair dryers, chargers, and more, so you can keep your bedroom neat and clean.

【Bottom Mount Drawer Slides】The drawer slides will guide the drawer open and close smoothly and effortlessly. Metal materials ensure sturdiness and durability, and the bottom mount design allows for an easy and straightforward installation.
【Simple Assembly Required】All of the required hardware, components, and illustrated instructions are comprised in the package so that you can easily complete the assembly in a short time.

【Durable and Sturdy】The 3-drawer nightstand is crafted of CARB P2-compliant MDF boards with a water-resistant veneer and is built in a cuboid shape, perfect for long use. Passed the load bearing test, our side table can hold up to 99 lb in total (Tabletop: 66lb. Each drawer: 11lb).

【Wide Applications】This 3-drawer side table is suitable for bedrooms, living rooms, bathrooms, offices, apartments, dormitories, etc. The classic appearance and useful storage will easily blend into any situation and home style, making your home more neat and chic.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Really nice nightstand
reviews.reviewText: The nightstand’s setup was incredibly easy and the instructions were clear. I’m surprised there aren’t more reviews, but I understand the 4/5 star rating now. It appears more expensive than its actual cost, and despite having no handles, it’s easy to open and close. It’s a great fit for small spaces, making it perfect for smaller rooms. Personally, I’d give it five stars.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The night stands came when promised. They were better than the expected quality and easy enough to assemble. Perfect fit for the bedroom they were gotten for. Yes, I would buy again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars cutest thing ever
reviews.reviewText: small but big (idk) best thing EVER, so cute with my little mushroom lamp. kinda hard to assemble but that’s probably because i’m noy good at building

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars A little difficult to assemble
reviews.reviewText: You really need to pay close attention to the instructions. There are no words, just drawings so you need to double check the orientation of all parts because a lot of them look very similar and you may need to disassemble and redo it. But after assembling the product looks very nice. Drawers are more shallow than it looks in the pictures, and sometimes they catch when you pull them out. Not as smooth as my Ikea drawers but can be expected with this price point. I would say purchase if you’re okay with smaller drawers and good at assembling furniture.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Screws don’t fit!!
reviews.reviewText: The little black screws don’t fit. Extremely disappointing, everything else was pretty easy. But it’s garbage.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: good quality for the price. The instructions aren’t that difficult you just have to pay attention to the drawings and take it step by step but they turned out great the drawers open and close smoothly I haven’t had any issues !

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewText: These small side tables are “ok”, the drawers are sturdy enough, but the base is not, and when you have the bottom drawer open it tips over. Need to find a way to add weight to the back or something to keep it from tipping over.
